We use Scorecard to measure digital consumption behavior data, which may include information about online activities, and video streaming activities, among other activities, as part of its broad market research efforts. For more information regarding Scorecard’s privacy practices please visit
here
.
Parse.ly.
We use Parse.ly to assess content performance. For more information regarding Parse.ly’s privacy practices, please visit
here
.
ComScore.
We use Comscore to assess the performance of our Servies. For information about ComScore’s privacy practices, please visit
here
