Extension to the EU-U.S. DPF, and the Swiss-U.S. DPF, Wunderkind commits
to resolve complaints about your privacy and our collection or use of your
personal data. European Union, UK or Swiss individuals with inquiries or
complaints regarding this privacy policy should first contact Wunderkind at
privacyrequests@wunderkind.co.
